    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニピの無人島ロケより少し前",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "雫、無人島ロケの日が迫ってるけど、準備は順調か？",
      "startTime": 2.2666664958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "準備は……バッチリ。議論に議論を重ねて\nそれぞれ必要なものを選んだから……",
      "startTime": 11.3333331625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、みんなで力を合わせて頑張ってるんだな\nそれは何よりだが……",
      "startTime": 18.6333331625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……？\nなんだか浮かない顔……どうかしたの？",
      "startTime": 23.1999998291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今回はサニピのみんなが熱望したから\nオファーを受けたが……",
      "startTime": 29.5999988119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "脱出成功率1パーセントなんて数字を聞くと\nどうしても心配してしまうんだよ",
      "startTime": 35.1999988119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 37.8000009496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "そんな風に心配してくれる人がいるから……\n私達も、無茶はしないようにしようって思える",
      "startTime": 43.3999998291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはほんとに心強い……\nさすがは星見プロの……お父さん？",
      "startTime": 50.7999998291,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}